<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">If you enjoyed reading Harold&apos;s tale, I heartily recommend &quot;The Love Song of Miss Queenie Hennessey&quot; to you. It will give you her side of the story an<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">If you enjoyed reading Harold's tale, I heartily recommend "The Love Song of Miss Queenie Hennessey" to you. It will give you her side of the story and more details on some of the characters, to boot. (Not saying any more as it would spoil it) but well worth the read too!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
