  <span id="freeText15218615325418415450" style="display:none">I find this book as uplifting but I could find any book with coming of age themes thrilling as long as it doesn't surround the theme of Alzheimer's. That being said, I also liked that it was set in Britain. I love British theme books and it really had me looking at Britain in a different light. I mean sure, its small compared to a state like Minnesota but when you walk the length of it you're sure going to have a journey in front of you.</span>
